<p>author: Marco Monteiro</p>

<p>categories: [books,laravel]</p>

<hr />

<p>The book is a guide to Laravel aimed at beginners to the framework who already have some PHP experience. It is structured in the form of guides to core features and stand-alone tutorials. It was written by a core developer of the Laravel framework, and has the support of the framework author.</p>

<p>Please note that this is a publish in progress title, eztra chapters may be added at a later date and it will be updated to support future versions of Laravel for free.
